snippet.title: qomp2  -  Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Break free and go on the journey of a Pong ball as you navigate your way through industrial mazes and dangerous obstacles. The follow-up to the surprise indie hit, Qomp, adds a new ability that opens up the way you play. Will you make it to the end? 

Qomp2 is coming soon. 

Wishlist today:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2243510/qomp_2
https://store.playstation.com/concept/10007565
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/qomp-2-switch/
https://store.epicgames.com/p/qomp-2-f3ee6d
